%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20Doodle%3A%20The%20history%20of%20the%20iconic%20temporary%20search%20logo%20illustrations%20and%20how%20to%20make%20your%20own%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Google%20employee%20sits%20in%20front%20of%20two%20screens%2C%20holding%20a%20stylus%2C%20while%20creating%20a%20Google%20Doodle%20illustration.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66460ba514fb5b23cc5d0575%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKimihiro%20Hoshino%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Google%20Doodle%20is%20a%20piece%20of%20art%20that%20temporarily%20replace%20the%20logo%20on%20Google's%20homepage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20first-ever%20Google%20Doodle%20was%20created%20as%20an%20out-of-office%20message%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-founders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20founders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20Doodles%20are%20now%20much%20more%20complex%2C%20and%20celebrate%20both%20major%20and%20obscure%20events%20and%20figures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20Google's%2025-year%20history%2C%20the%20Google%20Doodle%20has%20grown%20into%20an%20iconic%20and%20beloved%20way%20for%20the%20search%20engine%20to%20celebrate%20holidays%2C%20historical%20moments%2C%20or%20notable%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Google%20Doodle%20is%20a%20themed%20illustration%20or%20artwork%20that%20temporarily%20replaces%20the%20Google%20search%20logo%20on%20the%20search%20engine's%20homepage.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20doodles%20have%20been%20elevated%20from%20simplistic%20drawings%20to%20elaborate%20artworks%20or%20even%20interactive%20games%20that%20both%20inform%20and%20entertain%20the%20billions%20of%20people%20who%20use%20Google%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Google%20Doodle%20has%20marked%20events%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpi-day-google-doodle-made-by-dominique-ansel-creator-of-the-cronut-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPi%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2030th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20world%20wide%20web's%20creation%2C%20the%20136th%20birthday%20of%20author%20Virginia%20Woolf%2C%20and%20even%20Google's%20own%20birthday%20(September%2027%2C%201998).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20Google's%20homepage%20features%20a%20%26quot%3BPi%20Day%26quot%3B%20Google%20Doodle%20with%20letters%20created%20out%20of%20apple%20slices%20and%20baking%20ingredients%2C%20with%20a%20whole%20pie%20representing%20the%20second%20%26quot%3Bg%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3BGoogle.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5aa9389e3be59f1d008b47e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20commemorated%20Pi%20Day%20in%202018%20with%20a%20Google%20Doodle%20featuring%20a%20pie%20baked%20by%20Dominique%20Ansel%2C%20the%20pastry%20chef%20who%20invented%20the%20croissant-donut%20hybrid%20%26quot%3Bcronut.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EGoogle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Google%20Doodle%20is%20also%20known%20for%20drawing%20attention%20to%20more%20obscure%20figures%20and%20events%3A%20It%20has%20celebrated%20days%20like%20the%2096th%20birthday%20of%20David%20Warren%2C%20who%20invented%20the%20black%20boxes%20used%20in%20aircraft%3B%20the%2080th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Moscow%20Metro%2C%20and%20the%20121st%20anniversary%20of%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20first%20Japanese%20railway%20timetable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20typically%20sticks%20to%20historical%20figures%20or%20events%20for%20its%20doodles.%20Although%20Google%20Doodles%20sometimes%20appear%20for%20celebrations%20rooted%20in%20a%20particular%20religion%2C%20like%20Holi%2C%20Tu%20B'Av%2C%20or%20Valentine's%20Day%2C%20the%20company%20eschews%20including%20religious%20symbols%20in%20those%20illustrations.%20This%20official%20policy%20means%20you%20won't%20see%20designs%20for%20major%20holidays%20like%20Easter%20or%20Kwanzaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Google%20Doodles%20aren't%20your%20thing%2C%20you%20may%20be%20out%20of%20luck.%20Google%20Doodles%20can't%20be%20removed%2C%20hidden%2C%20or%20disabled.%20You'll%20just%20have%20to%20wait%20until%20the%20next%20day%20when%20it%20reverts%20to%20the%20standard%20Google%20logo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20to%20know%20about%20where%20the%20iconic%20Google%20Doodles%20come%20from%2C%20how%20to%20make%20one%2C%20and%20how%20they've%20changed%20over%20the%20years%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220082ce22-16b7-4f34-af28-895807c641f9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20first%20Google%20Doodle%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20very%20first%20Google%20Doodle%20was%20created%20by%20Google's%20founders%20in%201998.%20The%20illustration%20served%20as%20an%20out-of-office%20message%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-page-google-career-life-education%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELarry%20Page%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsergey-brin-career-life-education%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESergey%20Brin%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20denote%20that%20they%20were%20attending%20the%20Burning%20Man%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20Google%20Doodle%20has%20evolved%20to%20be%20more%20than%20just%20a%20simple%20logo%20and%20transformed%20to%20be%20interactive%20and%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222046%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20very%20first%20Google%20Doodle%20featured%20Google's%201998%20logo%20with%20a%20sketch%20of%20a%20blue%20stick%20figure%20behind%20the%20second%20%26quot%3Bo%26quot%3B%20in%20honor%20of%20the%20Burning%20Man%20festival.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664625a49fc063e829b1be6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22894%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first-ever%20Google%20Doodle%20debuted%20in%201998%20in%20honor%20of%20Burning%20Man.%3Cp%3EGoogle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a513908-c8ac-4687-be43-e838224cc48f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20make%20a%20Google%20Doodle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20Google's%20computer%20science%20education%20offerings%2C%20Google%20offers%20a%20short%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcsfirst.withgoogle.com%2Fc%2Fcs-first%2Fen%2Fcreate-your-own-google-logo%2Fcreate-your-own-google-logo%2Fcreate-your-own-google-logo.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etutorial%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20users%20can%20program%20their%20very%20own%20Google%20Doodles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you're%20a%20student%20between%20kindergarten%20and%20grade%2012%2C%20Google%20holds%20a%20Doodle%20for%20Google%20contest%20for%20students%20to%20create%20their%20own%20Google%20Doodle%20artwork%20and%20submit%20it%20for%20a%20chance%20to%20win%20awards%2C%20scholarships%2C%20and%20Google%20hardware%20and%20swag.%20The%20winner%20gets%20to%20have%20their%20artwork%20featured%20on%20Google's%20homepage%20for%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20enter%20the%20student%20competition%2C%20create%20your%20artwork%20out%20of%20any%20materials%20you%20like%20(Google%20even%20accepts%20pieces%20made%20from%20%26quot%3Bcrayons%2C%20clay%2C%20to%20found%20objects%26quot%3B)%20and%20write%20an%20artist's%20statement.%20You%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoodles.google.com%2Fd4g%2Fhow-it-works%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubmit%20your%20Google%20Doodle%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20mail%20or%20upload%20it%20as%20a%20jpg%20or%20png%20file.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202023%20Doodle%20for%20Google%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Fsearch%2Fmeet-rebecca-the-2023-doodle-for-google-national-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%