%2C%20as%20global%20investors'%20rush%20into%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20theme%20starts%20to%20leave%20pricey%20old-economy%20tech%20stocks%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20counterparts%20in%20the%20developed%20world%20and%20China%2C%20Indian%20software%20makers%20including%20leader%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20Ltd.%20have%20yet%20to%20make%20significant%20advances%20in%20generative%20AI.%20That%20combined%20with%20a%20still%20cloudy%20outlook%20for%20client%20spending%20may%20soon%20leave%20them%20looking%20like%20the%20tech%20bets%20of%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditional%20software%20companies'%20earnings%20and%20valuations%20are%20at%20risk%20because%20their%20business%20models%20are%20not%20evolving%20with%20the%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Deven%20Choksey%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20DRChoksey%20FinServ%20Pvt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20BSE%20Ltd.%20gauge%20of%20Indian%20software%20stocks%20has%20recently%20fallen%20through%20key%20support%20levels%20into%20a%20technical%20correction.%20Yet%20it's%20still%20trading%20well%20above%20its%20historical%20average%20earnings%20multiple%20after%20a%20yearslong%20rally%20in%20the%20nation's%20equity%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20IT%20firms%20enjoyed%20years%20of%20strong%20growth%20as%20the%20world's%20biggest%20corporations%20outsourced%20a%20vast%20amount%20of%20back-office%20work%20to%20save%20money%2C%20in%20a%20phenomenon%20known%20as%20getting%20%26quot%3BBangalored%26quot%3B.%20Those%20revenues%20have%20been%20slowing%20more%20recently%20as%20overseas%20customers%20cut%20spending%20to%20cope%20with%20challenging%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20software%20and%20internet%20majors%20such%20as%20Microsoft%20Corp.%20and%20Alphabet%20Inc.%20have%20been%20investing%20billions%20to%20develop%20their%20own%20cloud%20offerings%20and%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCoding%20is%20getting%20left%20behind%20by%20computing%20in%20the%20tech%20investing%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Choksey.%20Indian%20firms%20need%20to%20reinvent%20their%20business%20models%20more%20quickly%20to%20embrace%20AI%20and%20deliver%20better%20software-as-a-service%20solutions%20and%20infrastructure%20like%20Amazon.com%20Inc.'s%20unit%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20does%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETCS%20last%20month%20reported%20its%20slowest%20annual%20sales%20growth%20in%20three%20years.%20Competitor%20Infosys%20Ltd.%20issued%20a%20tepid%20forecast%20for%20revenue%20growth%20of%201%25%20to%203%25%20in%20the%20year%20through%20March%202025%20on%20a%20constant-currency%20basis%2C%20eliminating%20the%20impact%20of%20exchange-rate%20fluctuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Indian%20companies%20and%20their%20peers%20around%20the%20world%20like%20Accenture%20Plc%20are%20making%20positive%20noises%20on%20AI%2C%20the%20sales%20contributions%20are%20still%20small.%20TCS%20said%20its%20AI%20pipeline%20doubled%20last%20quarter%20to%20%24900%20million%20-%20that%20compares%20with%20its%20total%20annual%20revenue%20of%20around%20%2430%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20volatile%20geopolitical%20environment%20and%20uncertain%20macro%20outlook%20continue%20to%20weigh%20on%20client%20spending%20priorities.%20The%20IT%20sector%20may%20see%20further%20downgrades%20after%20sales%20missed%20expectations%20last%20quarter%2C%20according%20to%20Jefferies%20Financial%20Group%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResults%20by%20IT%20firms%20disappointed%20on%20the%20top%20line%2C%20and%20management%20commentary%20points%20to%20a%20weaker-than-expected%20growth%20outlook%2C%26quot%3B%20analysts%20Akshat%20Agarwal%20and%20Ankur%20Pant%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20dated%20May%207.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20up%20to%207%25%20cuts%20to%20consensus%20estimates%20last%20month%2C%20we%20see%20further%20risks%20to%20earnings%2C%20limiting%20upside%26quot%3B%20in%20share%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELofty%20valuations%20also%20point%20to%20caution.%20T