20in%20Iran's%20Isfahan%20province%20that%20also%20hosts%20a%20uranium%20enrichment%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20helicopter%20crash%20that%20killed%20the%20Iranian%20president%20is%20bound%20to%20spark%20a%20wave%20of%20speculation.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20reports%20in%20state%20media%20have%20referred%20to%20the%20crash%20as%20an%20accident%2C%20but%20an%20official%20word%20from%20the%20Iranian%20government%20is%20awaited.%20Anything%20that%20points%20to%20foul%20play%20may%20escalate%20tensions%20in%20the%20sensitive%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20equations%20with%20other%20countries%20are%20likely%20to%20remain%20the%20same%2C%20with%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20calling%20the%20shots.%20The%20government%20has%20already%20said%20it%20will%20operate%20without%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20US%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20a%20strong%20ally%20of%20Israel%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20news%20of%20Raisi's%20death%2C%20but%20earlier%20reports%20had%20said%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20been%20briefed%20about%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20few%20years%20have%20seen%20critical%20developments%20in%20US-Iran%20ties%20over%20Tehran's%20nuclear%20push.%20In%202018%2C%20then%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20withdrew%20from%20the%20Joint%20Comprehensive%20Plan%20Of%20Action%20--%20an%20agreement%20on%20Iranian%20nuclear%20programme%20--%20and%20restored%20harsh%20sanctions%20on%20Tehran.%20This%20prompted%20Iran%20to%20violate%20the%20agreement's%20nuclear%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2063-year-old%20Raisi%20took%20over%20in%202021%2C%20he%20took%20a%20tough%20stance%20in%20negotiations%2C%20seeing%20a%20chance%20to%20win%20broad%20relief%20from%20US%20sanctions%20in%20return%20for%20modest%20curbs%20on%20its%20increasingly%20advanced%20technology%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Reuters%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Asia%20conflict%20raised%20tensions.%20Despite%20its%20strong%20ties%20with%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%20has%20of%20late%20tried%20to%20de-escalate%20the%20situation%2C%20apparently%20over%20the%20rising%20human%20cost%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20Biden%20went%20as%20far%20as%20threatening%20to%20stop%20arms%20supplies%20to%20Israel%20if%20it%20invades%20the%20Gaza%20city%20of%20Rafah%2C%20prompting%20a%20sharp%20response%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20had%20also%20claimed%20that%20top%20Biden%20administration%20officials%20were%20in%20indirect%20talks%20with%20their%20Iranian%20counterparts%20to%20avoid%20escalating%20regional%20attacks.%20With%20Raisi's%20death%20threatening%20to%20further%20destablise%20the%20region%2C%20the%20US%20will%20look%20to%20ensure%20peace%20in%20the%20volatile%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20India%20Position%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20saddened%20and%20shocked%20by%20the%20tragic%20demise%20of%20Dr.%20Seyed%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%2C%20President%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHis%20contribution%20to%20strengthening%20India-Iran%20bilateral%20relationship%20will%20always%20be%20remembered.%20My%20heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Iran.%20India%20stands%20with%20Iran%20in%20this%20time%20of%20sorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crash%20that%20killed%20Raisi%20comes%20a%20week%20after%20New%20Delhi%20signed%20a%20contract%20with%20Iran%20to%20operate%20the%20Chabahar%20port%2C%20aimed%20at%20expanding%20trade%20with%20Central%20Asia.%20India%20had%20first%20proposed%20this%20plan%20back%20in%202003%2C%20but%20US%20sanctions%20on%20Iran%20over%20its%20suspected%20nuclear%20programme%20slowed%20down%20the%20port's%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pact%20drew%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20US%2C%20with%20Department%20of%20State%20spokesperson%20Vedant%20Patel%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Banyone%20considering%20business%20deals%20with%20Iran%26quot%3B%20needs%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20potential%20risk%20of%20sanctions%26quot%3B.%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20responded%20that%20the%20port%20would%20benefit%20the%20entire%20region%20and%20a%20narrow%20view%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20on%20it.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20even%20the%20US's%20own%20attitude%20to%20Chabahar%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20US%20has%20been%20appreciative%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20Chabahar%20has%20a%20larger%20relevance.%20We%20will%20work%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20India%20has%20strong%20relations%20with%20Israel%20too%2C%20and%20Tel%20Aviv%20had%20appreciated%20New%20Delhi's%20support%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716183180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fpar0cek8_ebrahim-raisi_625x300_20_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Febrahim-raisi-iran-presidents-death-iran-presidents-death-a-spark-in-tinderbox-geopolitical-impact-explained-5702872%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Iran%20mourns%20its%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%20Hossein%20Amir-Abdollahian%20and%20other%20officials%20killed%20in%20a%20helicopter%20crash%2C%20the%20world%20will%20be%20closely%20watching%20the%20aftermath%20and%20the%20implications%20on%20geopolitical%20equations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Febrahim-raisi-iran-presidents-death-iran-presidents-death-a-spark-in-tinderbox-geopolitical-impact-explained-5702872%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Febrahim-raisi-iran-presidents-death-iran-presidents-death-a-spark-in-tinderbox-geopolitical-impact-expla