tle%22%3A%22All%20About%20The%20Chopper%20That%20Crashed%2C%20Killing%20Iran%20President%2C%20Foreign%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Bell%20212%20helicopter%20carrying%20Iran's%20president%20and%20foreign%20minister%20crashed%20on%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20Iranian%20state%20media%2C%20as%20it%20flew%20through%20mountains%20in%20heavy%20fog.%20All%20are%20feared%20dead%2C%20an%20Iranian%20official%20said%20on%20Monday%20as%20search%20teams%20located%20the%20wreckage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civilian%20version%20of%20the%20ubiquitous%20Vietnam%20War-era%20UH-1N%20%26quot%3BTwin%20Huey%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20are%20in%20wide%20use%20globally%20by%20both%20governments%20and%20private%20operators%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWHAT%20ARE%20THE%20HELICOPTER'S%20ORIGINS%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBell%20Helicopter%20(now%20Bell%20Textron%2C%20a%20division%20of%20Textron%20Inc)%20developed%20the%20aircraft%20for%20the%20Canadian%20military%20in%20the%20late%201960s%20as%20an%20upgrade%20of%20the%20original%20UH-1%20Iroquois.%20The%20new%20design%20used%20two%20turboshaft%20engines%20instead%20of%20one%2C%20giving%20it%20greater%20carrying%20capacity.%20The%20helicopter%20was%20introduced%20in%201971%20and%20quickly%20adopted%20by%20both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Canada%2C%20according%20to%20U.S.%20military%20training%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWHAT%20ARE%20ITS%20USES%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20utility%20helicopter%20-%20the%20UH%20in%20its%20military%20designation%20represents%20those%20words%20-%20the%20Bell%20212%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20adaptable%20to%20all%20sorts%20of%20situations%2C%20including%20carrying%20people%2C%20deploying%20aerial%20firefighting%20gear%2C%20ferrying%20cargo%20and%20mounting%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iranian%20model%20that%20crashed%20on%20Sunday%20was%20configured%20to%20carry%20government%20passengers.%20Bell%20Helicopter%20advertises%20the%20latest%20version%2C%20the%20Subaru%20Bell%20412%2C%20for%20police%20use%2C%20medical%20transport%2C%20troop%20transport%2C%20the%20energy%20industry%20and%20firefighting.%20According%20to%20its%20type%20certification%20documents%20with%20the%20European%20Union%20Aviation%20Safety%20Agency%2C%20it%20can%20carry%2015%20people%2C%20including%20the%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWHICH%20ORGANISATIONS%20OPERATE%20THE%20HELICOPTER%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-military%20organisations%20that%20fly%20the%20Bell%20212%20include%20Japan's%20Coast%20Guard%3B%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20and%20fire%20departments%20in%20the%20United%20States%3B%20Thailand's%20national%20police%3B%20and%20many%20others.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20many%20Iran's%20government%20operates%2C%20but%20its%20air%20force%20and%20navy%20have%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C%20according%20to%20FlightGlobal's%202024%20World%20Air%20Forces%20directory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHAVE%20THERE%20BEEN%20OTHER%20INCIDENTS%20INVOLVING%20THE%20BELL%20212%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20fatal%20crash%20of%20a%20Bell%20212%20was%20in%20September%202023%2C%20when%20a%20privately%20operated%20aircraft%20crashed%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Flight%20Safety%20Foundation%2C%20a%20non-profit%20focusing%20on%20aviation%20safety.%20The%20most%20recent%20Iranian%20crash%20of%20the%20type%20was%20in%202018%2C%20killing%20four%20people%2C%20according%20to%20the%20organisation's%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716182520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fkspm721g_iran-president-helicopter_625x300_20_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-we-know-about-the-crashed-helicopter-that-was-carrying-iran-president-5702265%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Bell%20212%20helicopter%20carrying%20Iran's%20president%20and%20foreign%20minister%20crashed%20on%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20Iranian%20state%20media%2C%20as%20it%20flew%20through%20mountains%20in%20heavy%20fog.%20All%20are%20feared%20dead%2C%20an%20Iranian%20official%20said%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-we-know-about-the-crashed-helicopter-that-was-carrying-iran-president-5702265%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-we-know-about-the-crashed-helicopter-that-was-carrying-iran-president-5702265%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-we-know-about-the-crashed-helicopter-that-was-carrying-iran-president-5702265%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Iran%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi's%20Death%2C%20Mohammad%20Mokhber%20To%20Take%20Over%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIranian%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Febrahim-raisi%5C%22%3EEbrahim%20Raisi%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20his%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20Hossein%20Amir-Abdollahian%2C%20died%20in%20a%20helicopter%20crash%20last%20night.%20The%20aircraft%2C%20carrying%20top%20officials%2C%20went%20down%20while%20crossing%20mountainous%20terrain%20in%20heavy%20fog%20while%20en%20route%20to%20the%20Iranian%20city%20of%20Tabriz%20following%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Qiz%20Qalasi%20Dam%20on%20the%20Iranian-Azerbaijani%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Iranian%20constitution%2C%20the%20death%20of%20a%20sitting%20president%20triggers%20specific%20protocols.%20First%20Vice%20President%20Mohammad%20Mokhber%2C%2069%2C%20will%20assume%20the%20presidency%20in%20an%20interim%20capacity.%20Mokhber%2C%20a%20seasoned%20political%20figure%20with%20close%20ties%20to%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20has%20a%20history%20of%20significant%20influence%20within%20the%20regime.%20He%20formerly%20headed%20the%20Setad%2C%20a%20powerful%20state-owned%20foundation%2C%20and%20holds%20advanced%20degrees%20in%20international%20law%20and%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Febrahim-raisi-helicopter-crash-iran-president-drone-video-claims-to-show-location-of-iran-presidents-chopper-crash-site-5701755%5C%22%3EIranian%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%20Dies%20In%20Chopper%20Crash%3A%20Iran%20Media%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20council%20consisting%20of%20Mokhber%2C%20Parliamentary%20Speaker%20Mohammad%20Baqer%20Qalibaf%2C%20and%20Judiciary%20Chief%20Ghollamhossein%20Mohseni%20Ezhei%20is%20tasked%20with%20organising%20a%20new%20presidential%20election%20within%2050%20days.%20This%20transition%20must%20be%20approved%20by%20Supreme%20Leader%20Khamenei%2C%20who%20reassured%20the%20nation%20that%20state%20affairs%20would%20continue%20without%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Mokhber%2C%20born%20on%20September%201%2C%201955%2C%20is%20a%20figure%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20Iran's%20political%20and%20economic%20spheres.%20He%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20first%20vice%20president%20in%202021%20following%20Raisi's%20election.%20Mokhber's%20tenure%20at%20Setad%2C%20an%20organisation%20initially%20created%20to%20manage%20properties%20confiscated%20after%20the%201979%20Islamic%20Revolution%2C%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20controversy%20and%20sanctions.%20In%202010%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20included%20him%20in%20a%20sanctions%20list%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20nuclear%20and%20ballistic%20missile%20activities%2C%20although%20he%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20list%20two%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELIVE%20Updates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Febrahim-raisi-iran-president-helicopter-crash-live-updates-wreckage-of-iran-presidents-crashed-helicopter-found-5702084%5C%22%3ENew%20Footage%20Shows%20Site%20Of%20Iran%20President's%20Helicopter%20Crash%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20the%20US%20Treasury%20Department%20included%20Setad%20and%2037%20companies%20under%20its%20control%20on%20a%20list%20of%20sanctioned%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetad%2C%20formally%20known%20as%20Setad%20Ejraiye%20Farmane%20Hazrate%20Emam%20(the%20Headquarters%20for%20Executing%20the%20Order%20of%20the%20Imam)%2C%20was%20established%20by%20an%20order%20from%20Ayatollah%20Ruhollah%20Khomeini%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20and%20predecessor%20to%20Khamenei.%20The%20directive%20instructed%20aides%20to%20sell%20and%20manage%20properties%20purportedly%20abandoned%20during%20the%20turbulent%20period%20following%20the%201979%20Islamic%20Revolution%2C%20with%20most%20of%20the%20proceeds%20intended%20for%20charitable%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%2C%20Mokhber%20was%20part%20of%20a%20team%20of%20Iranian%20officials%20who%20visited%20Moscow%20in%20October%20last%20year%20and%20agreed%20to%20supply%20surface-to-surface%20missiles%20and%20more%20drones%20to%20Russia's%20military.%20The%20Iranian%20touring%20party%20also%20included%20two%20senior%20officials%20from%20the%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20and%20an%20official%20from%20the%20Supreme%20National%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20death%20of%20Raisi%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20close%20but%20uncharismatic%20ally%20of%20Khamenei%2C%20could%20significantly%20alter%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20within%20Iran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20death%2C%20besides%20Mokhber%2C%20opens%20the%20field%20for%20other%20contenders%2C%20including%20Parliamentary%20Speaker%20Mohammad%20Baqer%20Qalibaf%20%2C%20who%20has%20long%20harboured%20presidential%20ambitions.%20However%2C%20Qalibaf%2C%20a%20technocrat%20with%20a%20history%20of%20corruption%20allegations%2C%20might%20face%20a%20challenging%20path%20to%20securing%20the%20presidency.%3