ate-run%20news%20agency%2C%20that%20a%20helicopter%20carrying%20Raisi%20and%20other%20senior%20Iranian%20officials%20was%20forced%20to%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bhard%20landing%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday%2C%20without%20providing%20further%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeavy%20fog%20and%20bad%20weather%20%E2%80%94%20and%20eventually%20nighttime%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20prevented%20rescue%20personnel%20from%20immediately%20reaching%20the%20scene%2C%20which%20led%20to%20several%20hours%20of%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20president's%20status.%20It%20remains%20unclear%20what%20caused%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran's%20foreign%20minister%2C%20the%20governor%20of%20Iran's%20East%20Azerbaijan%20province%2C%20and%20other%20officials%20were%20also%20on%20board%20the%20helicopter.%20The%20high-level%20Iranian%20delegation%20was%20returning%20from%20a%20ceremony%20marking%20a%20dam%20opening%20near%20Azerbaijan's%20border.%20IRNA%20reported%20that%20two%20other%20helicopters%20carrying%20ministers%20and%20other%20officials%20who%20attended%20the%20ceremony%20reached%20their%20destinations%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran's%20vice%20president%2C%20Mohammad%20Mokhber%2C%20is%20next%20in%20line%20for%20the%20presidency.%20Al%20Jazeera%20reported%20that%20Mokhber%20would%20take%20over%20until%20new%20elections%20could%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22236d64e5-d6d1-401e-a950-cb53e178ec04%5C%22%3EWho%20was%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIran%20elected%20Raisi%2C%2063%2C%20in%202021%20after%20an%20election%20that%20saw%20the%20lowest%20voter%20turnout%20in%20the%20country's%20history%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Firan-helicopter-raisi-b483ba75e4339cfb0fe00c7349d023b8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaisi%20is%20considered%20a%20%26quot%3Bhard-liner%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bprot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%26quot%3B%20of%20Iranian%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20%E2%80%94%20the%20man%20who%20actually%20wields%20power%20in%20the%20country.%20Some%20analysts%20previously%20suggested%20Raisi%20could%20have%20replaced%20Kahmenei%20after%20his%20death%20or%20resignation%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaisi%20has%20led%20Iran%20through%20heightened%20tensions%20in%20the%20region%2C%20including%20the%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%20Iran%20is%20one%20of%20Hamas'%20primary%20patron%20states%2C%20and%20has%20carried%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fjordan-foils-arms-plot-kingdom-caught-iran-israel-shadow-war-2024-05-15%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20shadow%20war%20with%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20heart%20is%20with%20the%20Iranian%20nation%20as%20a%20friend%20and%20brother%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamas%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20Iran's%20state-run%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Iran%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-mimicked-russian-tactics-israel-attack-war-experts-say-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20a%20barrage%20of%20missiles%20toward%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20direct%20attack.%20Most%20of%20those%20attacks%20were%20intercepted%20and%20ultimately%20caused%20little%20damage.%20It%20was%20a%20response%20to%20Israel's%20attack%20on%20an%20Iranian%20consulate%20building%20in%20Damascus%20on%20April%201%2C%20which%20killed%20multiple%20high-level%20Iranian%20commanders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20sanctioned%20Raisi%20in%202019%20for%20human%20rights%20violations%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20commission%26quot%3B%20that%20ordered%20the%20execution%20of%20thousands%20of%20political%20prisoners%20in%20the%20late%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20era%2C%20Iran%20subjected%20thousands%20of%20political%20dissidents