0Raisi%3A%20The%20Hardline%20Iran%20President%20Who%20Died%20In%20Helicopter%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIranian%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%20died%20after%20his%20helicopter%20crashed%20in%20the%20mountains%20yesterday.%20Raisi%20was%20in%20line%20to%20be%20Iran's%20next%20supreme%20leader%2C%20along%20with%20a%20clampdown%20on%20morality%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaisi's%20hardline%20position%20had%20been%20all%20pervasive%20in%20domestic%20politics%20while%20he%20governed%20through%20a%20severe%20economic%20crisis%20and%20a%20historic%20escalation%20of%20the%20country's%20conflict%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaisi%20took%20over%20as%20president%20in%202021%2C%20succeeding%20the%20moderate%20Hassan%20Rouhani%2C%20for%20a%20term%20marked%20by%20crisis%20and%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20Of%20Morality%20Police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaisi%20was%20personally%20involved%20in%20two%20of%20the%20darkest%20periods%20of%20Iranian%20repression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20after%20his%20election%2C%20the%20mid-ranking%20cleric%20ordered%20that%20authorities%20tighten%20the%20enforcement%20of%20Iran's%20%26quot%3Bhijab%20and%20chastity%20law%26quot%3B%20restricting%20women's%20attire%20and%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20saw%20a%20wave%20of%20protests%20triggered%20by%20the%20death%20in%20custody%20of%20Iranian-Kurdish%20woman%20Mahsa%20Amini%20in%20September%202022%20after%20her%20arrest%20for%20allegedly%20flouting%20dress%20rules%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nationwide%20protests%20presented%20one%20of%20the%20gravest%20challenges%20to%20Iran's%20clerical%20rulers%20since%20the%201979%20Islamic%20Revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20were%20killed%2C%20according%20to%20rights%20groups%2C%20including%20dozens%20of%20security%20personnel%20who%20were%20part%20of%20a%20fierce%20crackdown%20on%20the%20demonstrators%20as%20the%20president%20insisted%20%26quot%3Bacts%20of%20chaos%20are%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Raisi%20Was%20Labelled%20'The%20Butcher%20Of%20Tehran'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Iran's%20exiled%20opposition%20and%20human%20rights%20groups%2C%20Raise's%20name%20evoked%20mass%20executions%20of%20Marxists%20and%20other%20leftists%20in%201988%2C%20when%20he%20was%20deputy%20prosecutor%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Court%20in%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInquisitions%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20committees%26quot%3B%20were%20set%20up%20across%20Iran%2C%20comprising%20religious%20judges%2C%20prosecutors%20and%20intelligence%20ministry%20officials%20who%20decided%20the%20fate%20of%20thousands%20of%20detainees%20in%20arbitrary%20trials%20that%20lasted%20just%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Amnesty%20International.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20number%20of%20people%20killed%20across%20Iran%20was%20never%20confirmed%2C%20Amnesty%20said%20minimum%20estimates%20put%20it%20at%205%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201988%20mass%20execution%20earned%20him%20the%20dubious%20soubriquet%20of%20'The%20Butcher%20of%20Tehran'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran-Israel%20Tensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20war%20sent%20regional%20tensions%20soaring%20again%20and%20a%20series%20of%20tit-for-tat%20escalations%20led%20to%20Tehran%20launching%20hundreds%20of%20missiles%20and%20rockets%20directly%20at%20Israel%20in%20April%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaisi%20recently%20emphasised%20Iran's%20support%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20a%20centrepiece%20of%20its%20foreign%20policy%20since%20the%201979%20Islamic%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20Palestine%20is%20the%20first%20issue%20of%20the%20Muslim%20world%2C%20and%20we%20are%20convinced%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Iran%20and%20Azerbaijan%20always%20support%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%20and%20Gaza%20and%20hate%20the%20Zionist%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Raisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Conservative%20Hardliner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEbrahim%20Raisi%2C%2063%2C%20rose%20through%20Iran's%20theocracy%20from%20hardline%20prosecutor%20to%20uncompromising%20president%2C%20overseeing%20a%20crackdown%20on%20protests%20at%20home%20and%20pushing%20hard%20in%20nuclear%20talks%20with%20world%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaisi's%20career%20started%20in%20the%20years%20after%20the%201979%20Islamic%20revolution.%20He%20was%20close%20to%20supreme%20leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Khamenei%2C%20Raisi%20often%20spoke%20up%20defiantly%20as%20Iran%2C%20the%20biggest%20Shiite%20Muslim%20power%2C%20was%20locked%20in%20a%20tense%20standoff%20with%20its%20declared%20arch%20foes%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Israel.%20Raisi%20has%20been%20on%20Washington's%20sanctions%20blacklist%20for%20complicity%20in%20%26quot%3Bserious%20human%20rights%20violations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaisi%20took%20a%20tough%20stance%20in%20the%20nuclear%20negotiations%2C%20seeing%20a%20chance%20to%20win%20broad%20relief%20from%20US%20sanctions%20in%20return%20for%20only%20modest%20curbs%20on%20Iran's%20increasingly%20advanced%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20then-US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20reneged%20on%20the%20deal%20Tehran%20had%20made%20with%20the%20six%20powers%20and%20restored%20harsh%20US%20sanctions%20on%20Iran%2C%20prompting%20Tehran%20to%20progressively%20violate%20the%20agreement's%20nuclear%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndirect%20talks%20between%20Tehran%20and%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20to%20revive%20the%20deal%20have%20stalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716179520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fev7307d8_ebrahim-raisi_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Febrahim-raisi-ebrahim-raisi-missing-ebrahim-raisi-profile-iran-president-who-is-iranian-president-ebrahim-rais