3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20his%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%2012.3%20million%20views%20and%20two%20lakh%20likes%20on%20the%20microblogging%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWt*%2090%25%20of%20the%20world%20subscribe%20to%20you%20bro%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BShould%20be%20streamed%20live%20on%20YouTube%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20happening%2C%20bro.%20Instead%2C%20challenge%20him%20to%20invest%20his%20efforts%20in%20his%20content%20as%20much%20as%20you%20invest.%20That%20will%20be%20much%20better%20for%20the%20Indian%20music%20scene%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistory%20repeats%20itself%20once%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fifth%20shared%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20only%20this%20would%20actually%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20just%20like%20to%20say%2C%20don't%20make%20the%20same%20mistake%20Like%20PewDiePie%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAnybody%20else%20remember%20the%20last%20time%20the%20biggest%20YouTuber%20went%20up%20against%20T-Series%20in%20a%20playful%20competition%3F%20It%20didn't%20end%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Gulshan%20Kumar%2C%20a%20music%20pioneer%20whose%20father%20owned%20a%20fruit%20juice%20store%2C%20established%20T-Series.%20The%20company%20came%20up%20with%20strategies%20to%20outperform%20its%20competitors%20and%20remain%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%2C%20from%20making%20cassette%20knockoffs%20of%20popular%20songs%20to%20entering%20the%20devotional%20music%20market.%20Since%20his%20death%20in%201997%2C%20the%20company%20has%20been%20headed%20by%20his%20son%2C%20Bhushan%20Its%20main%20office%20is%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET-Series%20has%20grown%20to%20over%20%24101%20million%20because%20Bhushan%20Kumar%20decided%20to%20embrace%20the%20digital%20age.%20In%20the%20e