owever%2C%20he%20was%20pronounced%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20suffered%20from%20asthma%20and%20type%202%20diabetes.%20His%20primary%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20listed%20as%20''myocardial%20infarction''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20Texas%20district%20court%20on%20Monday%2C%20states%20that%20his%20death%20was%20''%3Cem%3Ecaused%20wholly%20and%20solely%20by%20reason%20of%20the%20carelessness%2C%20recklessness%2C%20and%20negligence%20of%20the%20defendant.''%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20crewmembers%20%26quot%3Beventually%20attempted%20to%20use%26quot%3B%20the%20plane's%20automated%20external%20defibrillator%20(AED)%2C%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Beither%20unable%20to%20properly%20operate%20the%20machine%20or%20the%20machine%20did%20not%20function%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fviewfromthewing.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F2024-05-13-Defib-NTexas-Complaint.pdf%5C%22%3Elawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20eyewitnesses%2C%20each%20time%20the%20AED%20gave%20a%20''clear''%20warning%20for%20people%20to%20step%20back%20from%20Greenidge's%20body%20so%20that%20a%20shock%20could%20be%20administered%2C%20a%20shock%20was%20not%20delivered.%20Instead%2C%20the%20machine%20simply%20kept%20advising%20that%20CPR%20should%20be%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''After%20Kevin%20died%2C%20I%20never%20heard%20from%20American%20Airlines.%20It%20made%20me%20feel%20hopeless.%20I%20want%20answers%20from%20American%20Airlines.%20I%20want%20American%20Airlines%20to%20take%20full%20responsibility%20for%20Kevin's%20death.%20I%20never%20want%20this%20to%20happen%20to%20a%20child%20or%20family%20again%2C''%20the%20teen's%20mother%20Melissa%20Arzu%C2%A0said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20about%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20suit%2C%20the%20airline%20also%20failed%20to%20pay%20her%20the%20advance%20%24113%2C100%20it%20owed%20her%2C%20per%20the%20company's%20policy%2C%20when%20a%20passenger%20dies%20on%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20flight%20attendants%20working%20for%20US-based%20airlines%20are%20required%20to%20be%20trained%20in%20CPR%20and%20in%20use%20of%20the%20automatic%20external%20defibrillator.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Airlines%20declined%20to%20comment%20over%20the%20litigation%2C%20but%20said%20their%20''thoughts%20are%20with%20Mr.%20Greenidge's%20loved%20ones.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716172680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fp4qj9mhg_american-airlines_625x300_01_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famerican-airlines-sued-after-14-year-old-dies-dies-on-board-due-to-faulty-defibrillator-5701874%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teen's%20mother%20alleged%20that%20the%20flight%20crew%20was%20slow%20to%20respond%20after%20she%20called%20for%20help%20and%20that%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20operate%20the%20defibrillator.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famerican-airlines-sued-after-14-year-old-dies-dies-on-board-due-to-faulty-defibrillator-5701874%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famerican-airlines-sued-after-14-year-old-dies-dies-on-board-due-to-faulty-defibrillator-5701874%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famerican-airlines-sued-after-14-year-old-dies-dies-on-board-due-to-faulty-defibrillator-5701874%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saudi%20Arabia's%2088-year-old%20King%20Salman%20has%20a%20lung%20infection%20and%20will%20take%20antibiotics%2C%20doctors%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716172353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110259512%2Cimgsize-878412.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsaudi-arabias-88-year-old-king-salman-has-a-lung-infection-and-will-take-antibiotics-doctors-say%2Farticleshow%2F110259367.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110259367.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKing%20Salman%2C%2088%2C%20diagnosed%20with%20lung%20infection%2C%20to%20undergo%20treatment%20with%20antibiotics%20at%20Royal%20Clinics%20in%20Jeddah's%20Al%20Salam%20Palace%20after%20falling%20ill%20with%20fever%20and%20joint%20pain.%20Saudi%20Press%20Agency%20reported%20the%20diagnosis%20and%20the%20medical%20team%20decided%20on%20the%20treatment%20program.%20In%20April%2C%20the%20monarch%20entered%20a%20hospital%20for%20medical%20checks%20and%20was%20later%20discharged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsaudi-arabias-88-year-old-king-salman-has-a-lung-infection-and-will-take-antibiotics-doctors-say%2Farticleshow%2F110259367.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsaudi-arabias-88-year-old-king-salman-has-a-lung-infection-and-will-take-antibiotics-doctors-say%2Famp_articleshow%2F110259367.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsaudi-arabias-88-year-old-king-salman-has-a-lung-infection-and-will-take-antibiotics-doctors-say%2Famp_articleshow%2F110259367.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Crore%20Jobs%20Created%20In%206-7%20Years%3A%20PM%20Modi%20To%20NDTV%20On%20Unemployment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDynastic%20opposition%20parties%20are%20so%20disconnected%20from%20the%20youth%20that%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20fathom%20the%20changes%20that%20are%20taking%20place%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%2C%20the%20PM%20spoke%20on%20a%20range%20of%20issues%2C%20including%20his%20roadmap%20for%20the%20future%2C%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20BJP's%20prospects%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20foreign%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20the%20opposition's%20allegations%20on%20unemployment%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20many%20new%20avenues%20of%20employment%20generation%20have%20been%20created%20under%20his%20government%20and%20data%20from%20various%20sources%20also%20belies%20the%20claims%20of%20his%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20all%20the%20infrastructure%20projects%20carried%20out%20by%20his%20government%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thing%20to%20know%20is%20that%20so%20much%20work%20cannot%20be%20done%20without%20manpower.%20Just%20spending%20%C2%A0money%20does%20not%20mean%20a%20road%20is%20built%20or%20work%20on%20the%20electrification%20of%20the%20railways%20is%20carried%20out.%20You%20need%20manpower%20for%20that.%20Which%20means%20employment%20opportunities%20are%20created.%20I%20can't%20see%20any%20issue%20or%20truth%20in%20the%20opposition's%20talk%20of%20unemployment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20dynastic%20parties%20can't%20understand%20the%20changes%20that%20are%20taking%20place%20among%20the%20youth.%20Before%202014%2C%20there%20were%20only%20a%20few%20hundred%20startups%20and%20now%20there%20are%201.25%20lakh%20such%20companies.%20Each%20startup%20employs%20many%20bright%20youngsters.%20There%20are%20100%20unicorns%20as%20well%2C%20which%20means%20business%20worth%20Rs%208%20lakh%20crore.%20And%20these%20are%20people%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2020-25%2C%20they%20are%20our%20sons%20and%20daughters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrides%20have%20also%20been%20made%20in%20the%20gaming%20arena%2C%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20India%20will%20be%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20field%20and%20young%20people%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2020%20and%2022%20years%20will%20show%20the%20way.%20Another%20emerging%20area%2C%20he%20stressed%2C%20is%20the%20shift%20from%20an%20entertainment%20economy%20to%20a%20creative%20economy%20and%20said%20he%20firmly%20believes%20India's%20creators%20will%20capture%20a%20significant%20share%20of%20the%20global%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGreen%20jobs%20are%20also%20being%20created.%20Look%20at%20the%20aviation%20sector.%20There%20were%2070%20airports%2C%20now%20there%20are%20150.%20My%20estimate%20is%20that%20the%20total%20number%20of%20aircraft%20in%20the%20country%20is%20600-700%20and%20an%20order%20has%20been%20placed%20for%201%2C000%20new%20planes.%20Can%20anyone%20even%20imagine%20how%20many%20kinds%20of%20people%20will%20get%20employment%3F%20Therefore%2C%20this%20narrative%20is%20being%20peddled%20by%20people%20in%20politics%20who%20only%20know%20how%20things%20were%2030%20years%20ago%20and%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20same%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Unemployment%20Halved'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20numbers%20to%20back%20up%20his%20claims%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20cited%20data%20from%20the%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%20and%20said%20it%20had%20shown%20that%20unemployment%20has%20been%20halved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PLFS%20data%20also%20states%20that%206%20crore%20new%20jobs%20have%20been%20generated%20in%20six%20to%20seven%20years.%20The%20Employees'%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20has%20also%20said%20the%20same%20thing.%20I%20ran%20a%20big%20campaign%20for%20government%20jobs%20as%20well%2C%20and%20these%20people%20(the%20opposition)%20keep%20shouting%20about%20employment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20a%20report%20released%20by%20the%20SKOCH%20group%2C%20PM%20Modi%20asserted%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20said%205%20crore%20person-years%20of%20employment%20have%20been%20generated%20every%20year%20for%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20And%20they%20have%20used%2022%20parameters%20to%20say%20this.%20It's%20backed%20up%20by%20research.%20All%20of%20this%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20the%20ground%20as%20well%2C%20it%20isn't%20restricted%20to%20data%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20eyeing%20a%20historic%20third%20straight%20term%20in%20office%20and%20has%20set%20an%20ambitious%20target%20of%20winning%20370%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20over%20400%20for%20the%20NDA.%20Four%20phases%20of%20the%20ongoing%20election%20have%20been%20completed%20and%20the%20fifth%20is%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716172320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fm3deaao_pm-modi-interview_625x300_19_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-crore-jobs-created-in-6-7-years-pm-modi-to-ndtv-on-unemployment-5699165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dynastic%20opposition%20parties%20are%20so%20disconnected%20from%20the%20youth%20that%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20fathom%20the%20changes%20that%20are%20taking%20place%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-crore-jobs-created-in-6-7-years-pm-modi-to-ndtv-on-unemployment-5699165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-crore-jobs-created-in-6-7-years-pm-modi-to-ndtv-on-unemployment-5699165%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-crore-jobs-created-in-6-7-years-pm-modi-to-ndtv-on-unemployment-5699165%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Says%20Opposition%20Plays%20Communal%2C%20Casteist%20Politics%20In%20Garb%20Of%20Secularism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20turned%20the%20Opposition's%20allegation%20of%20communal%20politics%20against%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20head%2C%20telling%20NDTV%20that%20the%20Opposition%20is%20not%20only%20communal%20but%20their%20politics%20is%20also%20riddled%20with%20casteist%20and%20vote-bank%20ideas.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20how%20they%20run%20their%20politics...%20I%20have%20thought%20sometimes%20that%20I%20should%20be%20careful...%20But%20now%20I%20think%20whether%20I'm%20labelled%20communal%20or%20not%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20anyone%20says%20about%20me%2C%20I%20will%20expose%20their%20sins%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20examples%2C%20he%20said%20his%20motto%20is%20%26quot%3BSabka%20Saath%20Sabka%20Vikas%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BSay%20I%20have%20given%20benefits%20to%20a%20village%20of%20100%20families.%20Then%20do%20not%20ask%20who%20belongs%20to%20what%20community%2C%20which%20caste%2C%20who%20has%20relatives%20linked%20to%20whom%20and%20who%20bribed%20someone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20social%20welfare%2C%20his%20idea%20is%20saturation%20--%20%26quot%3B100%20per%20cent%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20--%20pointing%20to%20his%20oft-repeated%20remark%20that%20there%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bno%20discrimination%20in%20governance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20say%20100%20per%20cent%2C%20it%20means%20true%20social%20justice...%20true%20secularism.%20No%20one%20has%20any%20grounds%20for%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20asserting%20this%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20people%20have%20faith%20in%20his%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20scheme%20to%20distribute%20free%20vegetables%20to%2080%20crore%20people%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20said%20give%20him%20and%20not%20him.%20I'll%20never%20do%20that%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20Opposition%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20even%20raided%20the%20SC%2FST%20OBC%20reservation%20issue%20for%20votes.%20They%20support%20vote%20jihad...%20all%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20secularism.%20I%20want%20to%20take%20off%20that%20mask%20show%20everyone%20how%20they%20are%20extremely%20communal%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20an%20Opposition%20party's%20manifesto%20claims%20that%20contracts%20will%20be%20awarded%20on%20basis%20of%20religion.%20%26quot%3BBut%20how%20can%20you%20do%20it%3F%20Suppose%20one%20has%20to%20build%20a%20bridge.%20One%20then%20has%20to%20check%20who%20has%20the%20expertise%20and%20experience%20and%20resources...%20If%20that%20is%20awarded%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%2C%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20my%20country%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wide-ranging%20interview%2C%20PM%20Modi%20rubbished%20the%20Opposition%20claim%20that%20the%20NDA%20will%20change%20the%20constitution%20once%20they%20have%20a%20majority%20over%20400%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BFirst%20things%20first%2C%20there%20are%20already%20400%20seats%2C%20from%202019%20to%202024%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP.%20NDA%20had%20won%20360%20seats%20and%20NDA-plus%20has%20consistently%20been%20above%20400%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BLinking%20400%20seats%20and%20Constitution%20is%20stupidity.%20The%20issue%20is%20they%20don't%20want%20the%20House%20to%20function%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716172200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fqelthntg_narendra-modi_625x300_19_May_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-says-opposition-plays-communal-casteist-politics-in-garb-of-secularism-5699654%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20turned%20the%20Opposition's%20allegation%20of%20communal%20politics%20against%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20head%2C%20telling%20NDTV%20that%20the%20Opposition%20is%20not%20only%20communal%20but%20their%20politics%20is%20also%20riddled%20with%20casteist%20and%20vote-bank%20ideas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-says-opposition-plays-communal-casteist-politics-in-garb-of-secularism-5699654%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-says-opposition-plays-communal-casteist-politics-in-garb-of-secularism-5699654%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-says-opposition-plays-communal-casteist-politics-in-garb-of-secularism-5699654%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20On%20How%20He%20Ended%20%26quot%3BMalai%26quot%3B%20Factor%20Associated%20With%20Infrastructure%20Projects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20detailed%20his%20government's%20massive%20focus%20on%20the%20infrastructure%20sector%20and%20how%20their%20steps%20differ%20from%20previous%20regimes%20in%20an%20extensive%20interview%20to%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20in%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20previous%20governments%2C%20spoke%20about%20the%20%26quot%3B'malai'%26quot%3B%20factor%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20earlier%20associated%20with%20all%20infrastructure%20projects%3A%20%26quot%3BInfrastructure%20was%20misused%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20past.%20Earlier%20it%20meant%2C%20the%20bigger%20the%20project%2C%20the%20more%20the%20'malai'%20(cream%20-%20a%20metaphor%20for%20corruption).%20So%2C%20the%20'malai'%20factor%20got%20stuck%20with%20the%20infrastructure%20and%20that%20destroyed%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20years%2C%20I%20saw%20infrastructure%20either%20on%20paper%20or%20on%20the%20foundation%20stones.%20When%20I%20came%2C%20I%20started%20a%20regular%20programme%2C%20PRAGATI%2C%20and%20I%20started%20reviewing%20the%20projects%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPRAGATI%2C%20an%20integrating%20and%20interactive%20platform%2C%20aims%20to%20monitor%20and%20review%20important%20projects%20of%20the%20government%20as%20well%20as%20projects%20flagged%20by%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM's%20'Four-S%20Mantra'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20outlined%20his%20'four-S'%20mantra%20-%20scope%2C%20scale%2C%20speed%20and%20skill%20-%20the%20driving%20factors%20of%20infrastructure%20development%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20scope%20should%20be%20very%20big%2C%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20in%20parts%2C%20and%20the%20second%20thing%20is%20scale%2C%20which%20should%20also%20be%20large.%20The%20speed%20should%20be%20in%20sync%20with%20these%20two.%20So%2C%20scope%2C%20scale%20and%20speed%2C%20and%20then%20there%20should%20be%20skill.%20If%20we%20can%20get%20these%20four%20things%20together%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20we%20achieve%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clarified%20that%20by%20speed%2C%20he%20means%20the%20speed%20of%20decision-making%20and%20not%20the%20speed%20of%20construction.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20my%20effort%20has%20always%20been%20that%20there%20should%20be%20skill%2C%20scale%2C%20speed%20and%20we%20shouldn't%20let%20go%20of%20any%20scope.%20And%20by%20speed%2C%20I%20don't%20mean%20construction%20speed%20but%20the%20decision-making%20should%20be%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGati%20Shakti%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20Gati%20Shakti%20scheme%20and%20how%20it%20is%20helping%20in%20infrastructure%20development.%20PM%20Gati%20Shakti%20incorporates%20infrastructure%20schemes%20of%20various%20Ministries%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20improve%20connectivity%20and%20make%20Indian%20businesses%20more%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20talks%20about%20our%20digital%20infrastructure%20but%20not%20much%20is%20said%20about%20our%20Gati%20Shakti.%20Be%20it%20any%20infrastructure%20project%20in%20India%2C%20we%20need%20to%20reduce%20logistics%20spending%20and%20increase%20logistic%20support.%20Gati%20Shakti%20is%20one%20such%20platform.%20When%20I%20first%20launched%20it%2C%20the%20chief%20secretaries%20of%20the%20states%20were%20very%20happy.%20The%20data%20that%20is%20there%20in%20our%20Gati%20Shakti%20platform%2C%20there%20are%201%2C600%20layers%20to%20them.%20It's%20a%20unique%20thing.%20It%20helps%20in%20infrastructure%20development.%20I%20feel%20we%20are%20progressing%20with%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUPI%2C%20Railways%2C%20Electrification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20listing%20the%20government's%20achievements%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20spoke%20about%20UPI%20(Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20that%20facilitates%20inter-bank%20peer-to-peer%20and%20person-to-merchant%20transactions)%2C%20modernisation%20of%20railways%20and%20government's%20spending%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20UPI.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20thing%20in%20the%20fintech%20world...%20I%20think%20we%20are%20spending%2010%20or%2012%20lakh%20crore%20to%20stregthen%20the%20infrastructure%20sector.%20That's%20a%20big%20jump%20in%20spending%20from%20the%20earlier%20government's%20Rs%202%20lakh%20crore%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20towards%20modernising%20the%20railways.%20Unmanned%20crossings%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20almost%20zero.%20Look%20at%20the%20improvement%20in%20the%20cleanliness%20of%20the%20railway%20stations.%20Then%2C%20the%20use%20of%20railway%20tracks.%20Earlier%2C%20there%20were%20either%20goods%20or%20passenger%20trains.%20I%20have%20added%20yatri%20(tourism)%20trains%20to%20that.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Ramayan%20sector%20trains%2C%20Dwadash%20jyotirlinga%20circuit%20trains%2C%20Buddha%20circuit%20trainsets%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20his%20government's%20focus%20on%20electrification%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20achieved%20nearly%20100%20per%20cent%20electrification.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20builld%20infrastructure%20and%20leave%20it%20at%20that.%20We%20plan%20for%20its%20optimum%20utilisation%20simultaneously%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment's%20Infra%20Push%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20set%20out%20a%20broad%20plan%20for%20the%20country%20to%20become%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047%20when%20it%20will%20mark%20100%20years%20of%20freedom%20from%20British%20rule%2C%20and%20development%20in%20the%20infrastructure%20sector%20is%20key%20to%20that%20objective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP's%20%26quot%3BModi%20ki%20guarantee%26quot%3B%20manifesto%2C%20released%20days%20before%20the%20country%20went%20to%20polls%2C%20includes%20plans%20to%20strengthen%20infrastructure%20to%20attract%20investments%20and%20create%20jobs.%20As%20per%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20manifesto%20%26quot%3Bplaces%20the%20spotlight%20on%20turning%20India%20into%20a%20global%20manufacturing%20powerhouse.%20This%20vision%20aligns%20with%20the%20government's%20'Make%20in%20India'%20initiative%2C%20seeking%20to%20attract%20foreign%20investment%2C%20boost%20domestic%20production%2C%20and%20enhance%20exports%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20interim%20Budget%20in%20February%20focussed%20on%20infrastructure%20and%20long-term%20reforms%20to%20drive%20growth%20as%20it%20increased%20the%20the%20capital%20expenditure%20outlay%20to%2011.1%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%2011.11%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716172200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fdelhi-meerut-expressway-eastern-peripheral-expressway_625x300_1527417185928.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-mega-exclusive-pm-on-how-he-ended-mala