0yourself%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20everything.%20You%20can%20have%20all%20the%20positivity%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20if%20you%20aren't%20actively%20working%20toward%20success%2C%20you're%20not%20likely%20to%20stumble%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20Lyons'%20top%20three%20tips%20for%20coaching%20clients%20gearing%20up%20to%20try%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c21b70a2-8372-4a24-9375-9f1e6744ea88%5C%22%3EStart%20with%20a%20side%20hustle%20%E2%80%94%20one%20you're%20an%20expert%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOK%2C%20maybe%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20an%20expert%20%3Cem%3Enow%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20pick%20a%20field%20you%20can%20reasonably%20develop%20expertise%20in%20by%20yourself.%20You%20can't%20really%20start%20an%20innovative%20bioengineering%20company%20without%20any%20background%20knowledge%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20go%20back%20to%20school%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20tons%20of%20platforms%20to%20develop%20and%20showcase%20your%20expertise%2C%20Lyons%20noted%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffiverr-vs-upwork-for-freelancers-side-hustle-income-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUpwork%20and%20Fiverr%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20she%20said%20are%20great%20ways%20to%20build%20a%20ramp-up%20to%20launch%20your%20own%20small%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20first%20coaching%2C%20when%20I%20was%20getting%20certified%2C%20I%20would%20charge%20people%20five%20bucks%20an%20hour.%20I%20needed%20the%20hours%20for%20certification%20more%20than%20the%20money%20because%20I%20was%20working%20full-time%20but%20then%2C%20even%20for%20years%2C%20I%20was%20supercheap%2C%26quot%3B%20Lyons%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20you're%20getting%20started%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20charge%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20get%20the%20experience%2C%20build%20up%20your%20clientele%20to%20show%20that%20you're%20capable%20%E2%80%94%20and%20