ia.com%2F333343%2Ffarmer-producer-organisations-fpos-small-farmers-bayer-increase-yield-profits-jardalu-mango%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edouble%20their%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Interestingly%2C%20these%20farmers%20have%20collectively%20generated%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20and%20Rs%2023%20crore%20in%20the%20last%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20so%20satisfying%20to%20see%20the%20impact.%20However%2C%20I%20still%20feel%20this%20is%20not%20enough.%20We%20want%20to%20increase%20farmer%20income%20to%20five%20times%20so%20that%20we%20do%20not%20lag%20behind%20progressive%20states%20like%20Maharashtra.%20In%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20I%20am%20planning%20to%20achieve%20this%20by%20helping%20farmers%20process%20their%20produce%20into%20value-added%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20SumArth.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715929972000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-4-1-1715870841.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349986%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prabhat%20Kumar%20runs%20SumArth%2C%20an%20NGO%20that%20has%20impacted%20the%20lives%20of%2025%2C000%20farmers%20in%20500%20villages%20of%20Bihar%20by%20helping%20them%20switch%20from%20outdated%20agricultural%20practices%20to%20new%20cash%20crops%20like%20onions%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20and%20sweet%20corn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A109%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349986%2Fprabhat-kumar-sumarth-ngo-bihar-horticulture-training-for-farmers-double-income-cash-crops%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Startups%2C%2013%20Years%3A%20Entrepreneurs%20Show%20What%20Goes%20Behind%20Building%20a%20Multi-Crore%20Food%20Startup%22%2C%22content%22%