e%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20share%20that%20during%20every%20crisis%2C%20it%20is%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20that%20has%20kept%20them%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20a%20brand%20that%20will%20outlive%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20idea%20of%20creating%20their%20own%20brand%20was%20so%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20value%20to%20people%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20outliving%20the%20founders.%20This%20led%20to%20Marico%20acquiring%20about%2054%25%20equity%20stake%20in%20the%20company%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22True%20Elements%20has%20a%20factory%20in%20Pune%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-300x291.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-500x484.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-768x744.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-150x145.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350256%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrue%20Elements%20has%20a%20factory%20in%20Pune%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20choose%20a%20partner%20who%20would%20align%20with%20our%20vision%20and%20understand%20health.%20We%20both%20were%20also%20clear%2C%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20would%20outlive