2C000%20petal%20lotus%2C%20and%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Subrat%E2%80%99s%20interest%20piqued%20in%20growing%20rare%20flowering%20and%20fruiting%20plants%20at%20home.%20With%20a%20simple%20google%20search%2C%20he%20read%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246852%2Frare-exotic-plants-saplings-propagation-urban-gardener-organic-vertical-hanging-garden-bhopal-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erare%20plants%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20warm%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20keeping%20rare%20plants%20inside%20my%20garden.%20Sometimes%20it%20is%20challenging%20as%20well%2C%20given%20the%20temperature%20here%20rises%20to%2046%20degrees%20in%20the%20summer.%20But%20this%20challenge%20is%20what%20exactly%20makes%20it%20fun%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20control%20the%20temperature%2C%20he%20has%20established%20a%20small%20greenhouse%20where%20he%20keeps%20new%20saplings%20for%202-3%20months%20to%20help%20them%20acclimatise.%20%E2%80%9CI%20introduce%20them%20to%20direct%20sunlight%20slowly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20Miyazaki%20mango%20plant%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20planted%20it%20directly%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20my%20house.%20Its%20sapling%20cost%20me%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20take%20any%20risk.%20I%20let%20the%20sapling%20settle%20into%20the%20soil.%20After%20two%20months%2C%20I%20added%20cow%20dung%2C%20bone%20meal%2C%20neem%20and%20mustard%20cakes%20to%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Subrat%2C%20growing%20rare%20plants%20is%20just%20a%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20his%20only%20treasures.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349615%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20Subrat%2C%20growing%20rare%20plants%20is%20just%20a%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20his%20only%20treasures.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20his%20parents%2C%20Subrat%20believes%20in%20giving%20traditional%20fertilisers%20to%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20fruiting%20plant%20requires%20nitrogen%20for%20leaves%20and%20stem%20growth%2C%20phosphorus%20for%20root%20development%2C%20and%20potash%20for%20flower%20and%20fruit%20growth.%20We%20get%20these%20nutrients%20in%20cow%20dung%20itself.%20I%20do%20not%20make%20any%20other%20fancy%20fertilisers.%20Cow%20dung%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Subrat%20does%20not%20aim%20to%20sell%20the%20Miyazaki%20mangoes%2C%20he%20does%20sell%20saplings%20of%20the%20rare%201%2C000%20petal%20lotus%20and%20other%20water%20lily%20varieties.%20Last%20year%2C%20he%20earned%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20through%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20grow%20any%20rare%20plant%2C%20one%20must%20do%20a%20detailed%20study%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20they%20require%20and%20the%20pot%20size.%20For%20