A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IFS%20Officer%20Is%20On%20a%20Mission%20to%20Save%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Endangered%20Plants%3B%20What%20Makes%20them%20Special%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20dusk%20sets%2C%20anyone%20who%20stops%20by%20the%20research%20wing%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20in%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Haldwani%20looking%20for%20IFS%20officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20him%20there.%20Instead%2C%20the%20officer%20can%20be%20found%20promenading%20through%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20campus%20which%20teems%20with%20abundant%20flowering%20plants%20and%20fruit%20trees.%20The%20sight%20of%20a%20glorious%20green%20carpet%20thriving%20at%20a%20height%20of%20300%20ft%20above%20sea%20level%20is%20baffling.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F163949%2Fjakkur-bengaluru-lake-pollution-cleaning-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especies%20of%20flora%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20you%20think%20reside%20within%20this%2025-acre%20land%3F%20Take%20a%20guess.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20850%20species%20and%20counting%2C%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20Chaturvedi.%20In%20this%20forest-like%20ecosystem%20that%20he%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20few%20years%20cultivating%2C%20bamboo%20and%20cactus%20befriend%20each%20other%2C%20while%20crickets%2C%20butterflies%20and%20insects%20stop%20by%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20to%20the%20honeysuckle.%20The%20air%20is%20crisp%20and%20the%20walk%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20Chaturvedi%2C%20who%20pauses%20to%20put%20his%20experience%20into%20words%3B%20then%20proceeds%20to%20say%20that%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20justice.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20most%20taken%20aback%20by%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20optimistic%20view%20are%20the%20naysayers%20who%20were%20convinced%20that%20this%20particular%20posting%20in%20the%20highlands%20of%20Uttarakhand%20